Menu Type
---------
The Menu Type specifies the kind of menu to be displayed.
Normally, a default value of 0 should be given so that the
menu manager will select a primary root menu appropriate
for the target display system. However, explicit types can
be utilized:

   0 - Environment Default      5 - Bar Menu
   1 - <Not Available>          6 - Pull-down Menu
   2 - Numeric Selection        7 - Pop-up Menu
   3 - Alphabetic Selection     8 - Display Only
   4 - Highlighted Selection
